Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次也咚咚咚地與大家見面的幸運頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主持人小神晶piko～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是助手小野大輔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光飛逝  已經進入第二十一回了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  終於要進入尾聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來讓我們趕快進入這個節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Magaare↓{\r}\N彎曲～吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（マッガーレ：和上次一樣在捏古泉）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……
